kenji akabane (赤羽根 健治 akabane kenji, born october 31, 1984) is a japanese voice actor. his first starring role was as kouji kabuto in shin mazinger shougeki! z hen and he also went on to portray the producer in the anime adaptation of the idolmaster video game series. in 2014, he provided the voice of dragon shiryū in the film saint seiya: legend of sanctuary, a role he said was "cool" and "serious".